Usage: get_ccopt_clock_tree_nets [-help] [<pattern>] [-in_clock_trees <trees>]
                                 [-net_types <leaf|trunk|top>]
                                 [-not_in_clock_trees <trees>] [-regexp]

-help                       # Prints out the command usage
<pattern>                   # pattern for clock trees to return
                            # (string, optional)
-in_clock_trees <trees>     # return nets only in these clock trees
                            # (string, optional)
-net_types <leaf|trunk|top> # return nets of this type (string, optional)
-not_in_clock_trees <trees> # return nets not in these clock trees
                            # (string, optional)
-regexp                     # use regexp matching instead of wildcard (glob)
                            # (bool, optional)